*modsecurity-crs-2.2.6-r1 (17 Oct 2012)

  17 Oct 2012; Diego E. Pettenò <flameeyes@gentoo.org>
  +modsecurity-crs-2.2.6-r1.ebuild, -modsecurity-crs-2.2.6.ebuild:
  Remove srl_rules as they are currently broken with ModSec 2.7. Thanks to
  Clemente Aguiar in bug #436982 for reporting.

  30 Sep 2012; Diego E. Pettenò <flameeyes@gentoo.org>
  modsecurity-crs-2.2.6.ebuild:
  Update dependency to ModSec 2.7 as per bug #436632.

